-the-machines-hall-of-fame-induction-alone-3530442">莫雷洛独自出席了一年一度的摇滚名人堂仪式</a>，代表 Rage Against the Machine 接受入堂仪式。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tim-commerford-says-he-doesnt-know-if-rage-against-the-machine-have-broken-up-im-the-bass-player-3591786">Tim Commerford 表示，他不知道 Rage Against The Machine 是否已经解散：“我是贝斯手”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
